ADS.tip1: Scary Teacher 3D is a fun but thrilling simulation game. Published by Z & K Games, it’s a scary simulation game where you get to prank your neighbor. However, that neighbor also happens to be your creepy high school teacher, Miss T. Pranking someone, especially a teacher, might not look nice but Miss T deserves it. She has been very mean to students and has made their lives a living hell while in school.
